Rating: 3
If you want them crispy, try this. Before baking, dip the fries in well-beaten eggs, dredge excess, then coat with a bread crumb mixture that contains the ingredients from this recipe (add some parmesan too if desired). Bake as indicated making sure the coating doesn't burn, and voila, crispy fries!

